article.linkText: Lane scores 20 in Prairie View A&M's 76-64 victory against Eastern Kentucky
article.story: RICHMOND, Ky. -- — Charles Lane Jr. scored 20 points as Prairie View A&M beat Eastern Kentucky 76-64 on Tuesday. Lane also had six rebounds and three steals for the Panthers (4-2). Nick Gazelas scored 16 points and added three steals. Charles Smith IV had 11 points and was 4 of 11 shooting (3 for 5 from 3-point range). Devontae Blanton led the Colonels (2-2) in scoring, finishing with 20 points and 11 rebounds. John Ukomadu added eight points and seven rebounds for Eastern Kentucky. In addition, Collin Cooper had eight points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
